---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Our Company - Sassify">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="About Sassify" 
      highlightText="Sassify"
      description="We're on a mission to empower businesses with innovative SaaS solutions."
    />
    
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-24">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-300 font-medium text-sm mb-4">
              Our Story
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">From Startup to Industry Leader</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Founded in 2015, Sassify began with a simple idea: to make powerful SaaS tools accessible to businesses of all sizes. What started as a small team of three passionate developers has grown into a global company serving thousands of customers worldwide.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Our journey hasn't always been easy, but our commitment to innovation, quality, and customer success has remained unwavering. Today, we're proud to be recognized as a leader in the SaaS industry, helping businesses transform their operations and achieve remarkable results.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              As we continue to grow, we remain dedicated to our core mission: empowering businesses with the tools they need to succeed in the digital age.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="Sassify Team" class="w-full h-auto" />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-24">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-300 font-medium text-sm mb-4">
              Our Values
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">What We Stand For</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Our values guide everything we do, from how we build our products to how we interact with our customers and each other.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Trust & Transparency</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                We believe in building trust through transparency. We're open about our processes, pricing, and policies, and we always strive to do what's right for our customers.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Innovation & Excellence</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                We're constantly pushing the boundaries of what's possible, seeking new ways to solve complex problems and deliver exceptional value to our customers.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Customer Success</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                Our customers' success is our success. We're committed to providing the support, resources, and tools our customers need to achieve their goals.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-24">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-300 font-medium text-sm mb-4">
              Leadership Team
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Meet Our Leaders</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Our diverse team of leaders brings decades of experience and a shared passion for innovation.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="rounded-full overflow-hidden w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Michael Chen" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Michael Chen</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-2">CEO & Co-Founder</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
                With over 15 years of experience in the tech industry, Michael leads our company with vision and passion.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="rounded-full overflow-hidden w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Sarah Johnson</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-2">CTO & Co-Founder</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
                Sarah's technical expertise and innovative thinking drive our product development and technology strategy.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="rounded-full overflow-hidden w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/67.jpg" alt="David Rodriguez" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">David Rodriguez</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-2">COO</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
                David ensures our operations run smoothly and efficiently, enabling us to deliver exceptional value to our customers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Join Our Team</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            We're always looking for talented individuals who share our passion for innovation and excellence. Check out our current openings and join us on our mission.
          </p>
          <a href="/career" class="btn-primary">View Open Positions</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout> 
